comments: Caldwell-Pope (DEN) grazes Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) off-arm during his attempt to pass, which is marginal.
Porter Jr. (DEN) cleanly deflects the incoming pass away from Giddey (OKC) before incidental body contact occurs.
Dort (OKC) reaches for the ball and makes clean contact with it to begin the dislodge before incidental contact occurs with Caldwell-Pope (DEN) in transition.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the out of bounds called on Dort (OKC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. The ball deflects off Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) foot prior to it going out of bounds. Possession is awarded to OKC.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) extends his lower body in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and makes contact with his leg, which trips him and affects his SQBR.
Wiggins (OKC) collapses his forearm as he absorbs the contact from Gordon (DEN) during his shot attempt at the rim.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) removes his extended arm from Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path when marginal contact occurs at the start of Gilgeous-Alexander's drive, which he can move through.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) gathers on his right foot and establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he moves.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) maintains a resting hand on Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) side as both players engage during the incoming pass, and the contact is marginal.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) briefly grasps Caldwell-Pope (DEN) off-ball, and marginal contact occurs as both players engage before the pass.
Porter Jr. (DEN) deflects the incoming pass intended for Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) as he makes incidental contact with his arm on the follow-through.
The ball is last touched by Porter Jr. (DEN) prior to it going out of bounds.
Murray (DEN) contests Wallace's (OKC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Wallace (OKC) does not maintain a legal vertical position when contact occurs with Murray's (DEN) shoulder during the driving shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) jumps vertically, and not towards Dort (OKC), as Dort initiates the incidental contact during his shot attempt near the basket.
Jackson (DEN) does not release the inbounds pass within five seconds.
Porter Jr. (DEN) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Wiggins (OKC) cleanly deflects the inbounds pass from Gordon (DEN).
Wiggins (OKC) swipes down and initiates contact to Gordon's (DEN) arm at the start of the drive that affects his SQBR.
Gordon (DEN) enters the lane prior to the ball making contact to the rim.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Holmgren (OKC) contests the driving shot attempt and the contact that occurs with Jackson's (DEN) arm after the release is marginal.
